channel.title: Age of Empires II
channel.description:
Well, I wanted to know if anyone here played it and wanted to get a game started. The only thing I will not do is play a game sharing a village, and I'd prefer not to face other people, but computers.
Also, I play using the Expansion pack. It's much better. If you want to play, add me on MSN: <Removed>
Oh, and finally, I don't care if you play Age of Empires I, III, or any other version out there. This is the only one I play, and will play.
~Lin
